This paper is primarily focused on improving interpretability in deep neural networks, which is a core topic in the machine learning community. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) since these fields heavily rely on deep neural networks.
